'''同性婚姻'''在[[伊利诺伊州|伊利诺伊州]]自2014年6月1日开始合法化。2013年11月20日州长帕特·奎因签署了同性婚姻法案，在2014年6月1日后生效。

此前，2011年1月31日奎因签署法案使得[[民事结合|民事结合]]在伊利诺伊州自2011年6月1日开始合法化。该法案还允许异性恋伴侣注册民事结合关系，并承认在其他司法管辖区签订的大致类似的法律关系，包括同性婚姻和民事结合。

2007年至2013年间同性婚姻法案在伊利诺伊州曾多次被提出。2013年1月法案提交到两院，2月[[伊利诺伊州参议院|参议院]]以34-21表决通过。2013年2月26日，伊利诺伊州众议院执行委员会以6-5表决批准该法案。<ref name="house-cmte-advances-bill">{{cite news|last1=Long|first1=Ray|last2=Guerrero|first2=Rafael|title=Illinois House committee advances gay marriage bill|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-02-27/news/chi-illinois-house-committee-advances-gay-marriage-bill-20130226_1_marriage-bill-gay-marriage-people-in-civil-unions|accessdate=2013-05-07|newspaper=Chicago Tribune|date=2013-02-27|archive-date=2013-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130606172528/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-02-27/news/chi-illinois-house-committee-advances-gay-marriage-bill-20130226_1_marriage-bill-gay-marriage-people-in-civil-unions|dead-url=no}}</ref>代表Greg Harris预计表决将不会通过，因而并没有要求在立法机关5月31日休会前进行表决，<ref name="no-vote-in-house">{{cite news|last1=Garcia|first1=Monique|last2=Huppke|first2=Rex W.|last3=Dizikes|first3=Cynthia|title=Gay marriage bill fails to go to vote in Illinois House|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/local/ct-met-illinois-gay-marriage-0602-20130602,0,5636005.story|accessdate=2013-06-01|newspaper=Chicago Tribune|date=2013-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601095406/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/local/ct-met-illinois-gay-marriage-0602-20130602,0,5636005.story|archive-date=2013-06-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>而是延长了最后期限直到8月31日立法会特别会议审批。这一期限进一步延长至2013年10月和11月的伊利诺伊州众议院和参议院的否决权会议上。<ref name="veto-session-looms">{{cite news|url=http://www.windycitymediagroup.com/lgbt/Veto-session-looms-as-marriage-organizers-push-for-last-votes/44317.html|title=Veto session looms as marriage organizers push for last votes|date=2013-09-09|publisher=Windy City Times|accessdate=2013-11-21|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203003729/http://www.windycitymediagroup.com/lgbt/Veto-session-looms-as-marriage-organizers-push-for-last-votes/44317.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年11月5日众议院以61-54投票通过了一项同性婚姻合法化法案(SB10)，达到所需的60票门槛。<ref name="passes-house">{{cite news|last1=Garcia|first1=Monique|last2=Long|first2=Ray|title=Lawmakers approve gay marriage in Illinois|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-11-05/news/chi-gay-marriage-illinois-20131105_1_illinois-senate-gay-marriage-gay-lawmakers|accessdate=2013-11-21|newspaper=Chicago Tribune|date=2013-11-05|archive-date=2013-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131123000257/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-11-05/news/chi-gay-marriage-illinois-20131105_1_illinois-senate-gay-marriage-gay-lawmakers|dead-url=no}}</ref>州参议院随即以32-21批准了修订后的法案<ref name="on-to-govs-desk">{{Cite web |url=http://www.suntimes.com/23558841-761/gay-marriage-bill-passes-in-illinois-house.html |title=Gay marriage bill passes in Illinois house, senate - on to governors desk |accessdate=2013-11-21 |archive-date=2013-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203001714/http://www.suntimes.com/23558841-761/gay-marriage-bill-passes-in-illinois-house.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，州长帕特·奎因11月20日签署了该法案使之成为法律。<ref name="quinn-signs">{{cite news|last1=Garcia|first1=Monique|title=Quinn signs Illinois gay marriage bill|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/chi-illinois-gay-marriage-bill-signing-20131120,0,4464600.story|newspaper=Chicago Tribune|date=2013-11-20|accessdate=2013-11-20|archive-date=2013-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131121023708/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/chi-illinois-gay-marriage-bill-signing-20131120,0,4464600.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>该法案于2014年6月1日生效，从而使同性伴侣在2014年6月2日（强制性的一天的等待期后）可以获得结婚证书。<ref name="q-and-a">{{Cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/local/ct-met-gay-marriage-qa-20131106,0,1827048,full.story |title=Gay marriage in Illinois: Q & A |accessdate=2013-11-21 |archive-date=2013-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109065633/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/local/ct-met-gay-marriage-qa-20131106%2C0%2C1827048%2Cfull.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>

